title: Another Epic Clash?
description:
Pablo Torre, Domonique Foxworth and The Ringer's Kevin Clark debate where they stand with the Suns after Devin Booker’s injury in the squad's Game 2 loss and if they see the Celtics and Nets having another epic game tonight.
